w1.notes:
* While {{tip|ground|grounded}} '''Zed''' can cast ''Living Shadow'' but may not swap places with it.
* The [[File:Zed's Shadow.png|20px|border]] ''Shadow'' grants {{tip|sight}} of its surroundings and is {{tip|untargetable}}.
* '''Zed''' always has an ''arrow'' next to him pointing in the direction of his [[File:Zed's Shadow.png|20px|border]] ''Shadows''. It has three different colors, each one symbolizes important information about the specific ''Shadow.'' They are only visible to '''Zed'''.
[[File:Multiple_Shadows_with_Arrows.png|thumb|250px|left|Two arrows point toward their corresponding [[File:Zed's Shadow.png|20px|border]] '''Shadows'''.]]
{{clear}}
[[File:Shadow_(Green_Arrow).png|thumb|250px|left|A {{Color|Green|'''green arrow'''}} ({{Color|Blue|'''blue'''}} in colorblind mode) means the [[File:Zed's Shadow.png|20px|border]] '''Shadow''' can be swapped places with.]]
{{clear}}
[[File:Shadow_(Yellow_Arrow).png|thumb|250px|left|A {{Color|Yellow|'''yellow arrow'''}} signifies the [[File:Zed's Shadow.png|20px|border]] '''Shadow''' is about to disappear.]]
{{clear}}
[[File:Shadow_(Red_Arrow).png|thumb|250px|left|A {{Color|Red|'''red arrow'''}} ({{Color|Orange|'''orange'''}} in colorblind mode) indicates the [[File:Zed's Shadow.png|20px|border]] '''Shadow''' is unable to be swapped places with.]]
